{"tid":2136470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【08.01】張竹君：看新聞才得知中共派員來港展開實驗室工作","createTime":"2020-08-02T07:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T18:02:06.000Z","uid":21470,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea3f30e97fe6e59471ddaa0bcb5d002944a79a8","tid":2136470,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"張竹君：看新聞才得知中央派員來港展開實驗室工作<br />\n最後更新時間 2020-08-01 18:07<br />\n<br />\n衛健委明天會派7名核酸檢測支援隊先遣隊隊員來港，展開實驗室工作。張竹君指，最近忙於做個案追蹤，是由新聞才得知中央會派員來港，不知詳情，但不代表整個衛生署也不知。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君指，早前曾表示香港沒條件進行全民檢測，是指當時的檢測能力，但如果有外來幫助，要再了解詳情才得知能否全民檢測。她解釋，如果全民檢測意思是本港700萬人全部要檢測，按目前每日檢測量1至2萬，是好難做到；但如果意思是針對某地區或人群的大型檢測，情況又會不同，因此要視乎實際安排。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2350125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2350125&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=faa045f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2350125</a>"},{"pid":"a9bec0bf5ed7db8dd6d233f18c5a241c41dd14b6","tid":2136470,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0852786e8a40c96840d78eea187c2dd8aca8d972","tid":2136470,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"西九龍影相手足被控襲警 聽朝9:30西九龍裁判法院提堂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2136461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2136461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7uALB7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7uALB7.jpg&h=a3c7ef28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQjEsRH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQjEsRH.png&h=006c9dac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"726757cd83510e63b44faccc0aa7a8d7c2193a49","tid"